        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A schedule of work set out in sufficient detail for it to be quantifiable, implemented and monitored. Can include contractual details relevant to the commissioning body. A project design may be a research proposal independent of the planning framework</skos:scopeNote>
      </skos:Concept>
    </skos:narrower>

    <skos:narrower>
