        <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A specification that sets out the scope of fieldwork and post-excavation methods required to understand the extent, character and significance of any archaeological remains within a planning application area. A WSI is generally produced in response to a project brief issued by the Local Authority Archaeological Officer.</skos:scopeNote>
